# Credentials — ignore email.txt only when it contains data (non-empty key/email)
# The empty template version is tracked by git.
# Once you fill in your key locally, git will still see it as modified —
# run this once after cloning to stop tracking local changes:
#   git update-index --assume-unchanged server/email.txt
